  {
    "hotel_id": "230697",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/palm-beach-hotel-resort/hotel/bali-id.html",
    "name": "Palm Beach Hotel & Resort",
    "detail": "I always stayed in this hotel whenever I traveled back home to see my family. I love its lush garden and its spacious room, more importantly its porch in each room. It always been memorable and enjoyable for me to just have a cup of tea in the morning in the porch. Its swimming pool is pretty big and well-maintained. Now, the additional spa is a plus, the price is just slightly higher than those outside the hotel but not much at all, particularly if I compare the price I pay in Australia. I have also worked at 5 star-hotels in Bali and Jakarta, so this hotel suits people who love the old Balinese charm, all rooms facing to the gorgeous green garden. All staff were attentive and looking after you well. It's just 5-10 minutes drive from the airport and a literally walk distance from the Jerman beach. I also just walked to the closest mall (Lippo Mall has everything you need on its basement supermarket). ",
